map_npcs.name: Seer Sister Aira
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Hmm, I see your future holds quite the adventures...
Perhaps come visit me after meeting my other sisters...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Ah, I knew you would reach me eventually...

map_npcs.name: Crew Tony
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Huh, the view up here sure is amazing, isn't it?
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Did you take that elevator up here? We just finished working on it!
Since I'm on break, do you wanna do a little battling?

map_npcs.name: Raider Chris
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
So you know those three Seer Sisters?
One of them has an Oochamon that'll clear the lightning ball.
I think it was orange... probably!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Bet you're wondering how to get past that ball of lighting, huh?
I'll tell ya what I know if you win!

map_npcs.name: Raider Zayla
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
*sigh* Sometime's its nice to just relax and watch the storm roll in...
It's not one of those times right now though, let's fight!

map_shops.greeting_dialogue: Welcome to my store. Buy whatever you need below!
